OL,3,CFerry officer loses appeal against
OL,4,Cjail sentence over fatal boat collision
OL,6,FA former Condor ferry officer who was
OL,7,Fjailed after three fishermen died off
OL,8,Fthe coast of Jersey has lost his
OL,9,Fappeal against his sentence.
OL,11,FLewis Peter Carr, from Sunderland, was
OL,12,Fin Jersey's Royal Court on Thursday 2
OL,13,FApril, to appeal his 20-month prison
OL,14,Fsentence for endangering ships,
OL,15,Fstructures, or individuals - contrary
OL,16,Fto Jersey's Shipping Law.
OL,18,FHe was at the helm of the Commodore
OL,19,FGoodwill when it collided with the
OL,20,Ffishing vessel, the L'Ecume II, in
OL,21,FDecember 2022.
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws         G1/4
