OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F385A1775747465
OL,3,CFerry officer loses appeal against
OL,4,Cjail sentence over fatal boat collision
OL,6,FThe trawler's skipper, Michael
OL,7,FMichieli and crewmen Jervis Balagat
OL,8,Fand Larry Simyunn died in the incident.
OL,10,FCarr appeared at the Royal Court,
OL,11,Frepresented by defence advocate Simon
OL,12,FThomas.
OL,14,FHis family flew to Jersey to hear the
OL,15,Fappeal; Michael Michieli's brother
OL,16,FRobert and a friend who was with
OL,17,FMichael the night before the collision
OL,18,Fwere also in attendance.
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws         G2/4
