CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F385A1775747465
OL,3,CFerry officer loses appeal against
OL,4,Cjail sentence over fatal boat collision
OL,6,FAdvocate Thomas tried to argue the
OL,7,Fsentence was manifestly excessive,
OL,8,Fciting Carr's good character.
OL,10,FHowever, Commissioner Alan Binnington,
OL,11,Fwho presided over the appeal hearing,
OL,12,Fsaid that the absence of a guilty plea
OL,13,Fmeant the sentence couldn't have been
OL,14,Freduced.
OL,16,FHe added that Carr prioritised non-
OL,17,Fsafety issues despite collision
OL,18,Fwarnings on the radar.
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws         G3/4
