PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F385A1775747465
OL,3,CFerry officer loses appeal against
OL,4,Cjail sentence over fatal boat collision
OL,6,FThe Commissioner also explained that
OL,7,Fthere was "a serious degree of
OL,8,Fnegligence and serious harm" which
OL,9,Fresulted in the deaths of the three
OL,10,Ffishermen.
OL,12,FAfter losing his appeal, Carr was
OL,13,Ftaken by police van back to La Moye
OL,14,Fprison.
